      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "table",
          "level": 3,
          "title": "Water Treatment Processes",
          "table": {
            "header": ["SUB-TOPIC", "SHORT DESCRIPTION / NOTES", "EXTRA"],
            "rows": [
              [
                "AERATION",
                "Removes dissolved gases (CO₂, H₂S) and oxidizes Fe & Mn\nImproves taste and odor\nMethods: Spray, cascade, diffused air\nO₂ transfer: O₂ transfer = K_L × A × (C_s – C)",
                ""
              ],
              [
                "COAGULATION & FLOCCULATION",
                "Purpose: Remove colloidal and suspended particles\nCoagulants: Alum (Al₂(SO₄)₃), Ferric chloride\nProcess: Chemical added → destabilizes particles → flocs form\nFlocculation: Gentle mixing to enlarge flocs\nJar Test used for optimum dose determination",
                ""
              ],
              [
                "SEDIMENTATION",
                "Removal of heavy particles by gravity settling\nSedimentation tank design:\nSurface overflow rate: V_o = Q/A (m³/s per m²)\nDetention time: t = V/Q (s)\nParticle settling velocity: V_s = (ρ_p - ρ) g d² / 18μ (Stoke's Law)",
                ""
              ],
              [
                "FILTRATION",
                "Removes remaining suspended particles after sedimentation\nTypes: Slow Sand Filter (SSF): 0.1–0.3 m/h, Rapid Sand Filter (RSF): 5–15 m/h, Dual Media Filter: Sand + Anthracite\nFilter design: Hydraulic loading: HLR = Q/A_f",
                ""
              ],
              [
                "DISINFECTION",
                "Purpose: Kill or inactivate pathogenic microorganisms\nMethods: Chlorination, UV, Ozone\nChlorination formula: Dose(mg/L) = C × Q / Flow\nFree chlorine residual: 0.2–0.5 mg/L (Nepal standards)\nContact time: C × t = 15–30 mg·min/L for effective disinfection",
                ""
              ]
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "formulas",
          "level": 3,
          "title": "Important Formulas – Treatment Processes",
          "items": [
